ðŸ” Core Philosophy

Preparedness Is a Human Right â€” Aerospace and information readiness shouldn't be limited to governments or militaries.

Knowledge Should Be Shared â€” Every module is open-source and designed to be replicated in rural, off-grid, and civilian scenarios.

Civil Defense Reimagined â€” This is about communities, not soldiers.



